        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="🏅战役"><a href="#🏅战役" class="headerlink" title="🏅战役"></a>🏅战役</h1><p>本关的关键点是使用援军和箭塔消灭萨满，避免萨满持续回血</p><p>科技树升级 3级箭塔 2级兵营<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/1.jpg"><br>开局先建4座箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/2.jpg"><br>建1座兵营<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/3.jpg"><br>继续建3座箭塔，用援军和兵营拦截敌人<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/4.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/5.jpg"><br>开始升级下方的箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/6.jpg"><br>直接用火雨消灭萨满<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/7.jpg"><br>继续升级靠下的2座箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/8.jpg"><br>把箭塔全部升到2级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/9.jpg"><br>上方建1座兵营，用于拦截食人魔和萨满，给兵营升级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/10.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/11.jpg"><br>上方兵营旁边补1座箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/12.jpg"><br>升级箭塔，在最后一个位置再建箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/13.jpg"><br>火雨攻击萨满通关<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/14.jpg"></p><h1 id="🏆英雄"><a href="#🏆英雄" class="headerlink" title="🏆英雄"></a>🏆英雄</h1><p>科技树升级 2级箭塔 2级兵营 2级火雨 2级援军<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/15.jpg"><br>开局3座箭塔，1座兵营<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/16.jpg"><br>火雨直接消灭土狼避免意外<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/17.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/18.jpg"><br>继续建2座箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/19.jpg"><br>再建2座箭塔，用援军拦截萨满，使其不能给敌人加血，并受到箭塔攻击<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/20.jpg"><br>第3波火雨消灭大批敌人，再建1座兵营，然后开始升级箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/21.jpg"><br>注意用援军拦截萨满，使其不能给食人魔加血<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/22.jpg"><br>第4波末尾用火雨消灭大部队<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/23.jpg"><br>持续升级下方的箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/24.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/25.jpg"><br>第5波用火雨消灭食人魔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/26.jpg"><br>第6波要用援军拦截下面出口的萨满，避免其与食人魔会和<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/27.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/28.jpg"><br>等食人魔汇集到兵营处时，用火雨消灭<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/29.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/30.jpg"></p><h1 id="🥇钢铁"><a href="#🥇钢铁" class="headerlink" title="🥇钢铁"></a>🥇钢铁</h1><p>科技树升级 2级箭塔 2级兵营 2级火雨 2级援军<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/31.jpg"><br>全部建箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/32.jpg"><br>用火雨消灭萨满<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/33.jpg"><br>下方<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/pagelasi/34.jpg"><br><img src="https