        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="🏅战役"><a href="#🏅战役" class="headerlink" title="🏅战役"></a>🏅战役</h1><p>科技树升级 2级法师 5级火雨<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/1.jpg"><br>开局建法师塔和兵营<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/2.jpg"><br>下方再建2座法师塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/3.jpg"><br>第四波火雨消灭萨满<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/4.jpg"><br>升级右边的法师塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/5.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/6.jpg"><br>火雨消灭土匪<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/7.jpg"><br>升级左边的法师塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/8.jpg"><br>火雨消灭萨满，避免其给敌人回血<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/9.jpg"><br>继续把法师塔升到3级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/10.jpg"><br>上方再建一座法师塔，后面打Boss的小兵有用<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/12.jpg"><br>上方建兵营和法师塔，拦住城堡入口<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/13.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/14.jpg"><br>升级法师塔到奥术防御塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/15.jpg"><br>右上方也再建一座法师塔，并升级到奥术防御塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/16.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/17.jpg"><br>Boss【毁灭者】出来直接用火雨打击<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/18.jpg"><br>升级下上方的兵营，避免傀儡头偷家<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/19.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/20.jpg"><br>火雨好了再次打击毁灭者，这也是我们升级5级火雨的原因<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/21.jpg"><br>很快毁灭者就狗带了<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/22.jpg"></p><h1 id="🏆英雄"><a href="#🏆英雄" class="headerlink" title="🏆英雄"></a>🏆英雄</h1><p>科技树升级 除了炮塔全部点到3级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/23.jpg"><br>城堡入口建2座军营，下方一边法师塔一边箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/24.jpg"><br>升级箭塔为游侠匿所<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/25.jpg"><br>然后游侠旁建法师塔，法师塔旁建箭塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/26.jpg"><br>火雨搞定高护甲的黑暗骑士<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/27.jpg"><br>游侠升级森林之怒<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/28.jpg"><br>大波土匪和强盗聚集的时候火雨消灭<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/29.jpg"><br>升级第2座游侠<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/30.jpg"><br>把兵营都升一级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/31.jpg"><br>然后上方两边都再补一座兵营<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/32.jpg"><br>大批敌人聚集的时候火雨落下消灭<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/33.jpg"><br>另一座游侠也升级森林之怒<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/34.jpg"><br>法师塔全都升到3级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/35.jpg"><br>然后2座法师塔升级到奥术防御塔<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/36.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/37.jpg"><br>第5波黑暗骑士聚集的时候火雨消灭<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/38.jpg"><br>上方兵营升3级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/39.jpg"><br>再次用火雨消灭一大波黑暗骑士<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/40.jpg"><br>把上方的兵营卖掉，在原来兵营的位置建造法师塔，用来打击掠夺者<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/41.jpg"><br>上方的2座法师塔也升级奥术<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/42.jpg"><br>下方可以再补一座法师塔并升级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/43.jpg"><br>敌人一聚集就用火雨消灭，下方法师塔升级奥术<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/44.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/45.jpg"><br>兵营升级圣骑士<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/46.jpg"><br>顺利通过<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/47.jpg"></p><h1 id="🥇钢铁"><a href="#🥇钢铁" class="headerlink" title="🥇钢铁"></a>🥇钢铁</h1><p>科技树升级 除了炮塔全部点到3级<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/49.jpg"><br>在法师塔周边各建3座兵营<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/51.jpg"></p><p>右边兵营升级到圣骑士</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/52.jpg"></p><p>升级神圣打击【关键】，然后就有AOE能力了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/53.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/54.jpg"></p><p>左边也升级圣骑士</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/55.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/56.jpg"></p><p>同样升级神圣打击</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/57.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/58.jpg"></p><p>有2座圣骑士后，开始升级2座法师塔为奥术防御塔</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/59.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/60.jpg"></p><p>继续升级下方兵营</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/61.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/62.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fun-game/img@master/Game-Island/kr/chengbaozhizhan/63.jpg"></p><h1 id="看看视频？"><a href="#看看视频？" class="headerlink" title="看看视频？"></a>看看视频？</h1><p>攻略打法来自B站<br>Up主：@DKてす</p><div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=213911798&bvid=BV1Xa411E7Na&cid=717276895&page=11" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"> </iframe></div>Up主：@准点到达<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=516183360&bvid=BV1Bg411a7fN&cid=851422724&page=23" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"> </iframe></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
